; Simple 150 x 100 mm box — use with scale = 0.001 in gcode.cfg
; Z > 0 → travel (position mode)
; Z < 0 → draw (admittance/force mode)

G00 X0 Y0 Z10       ; travel to start, lifted
G01 X0 Y0 Z-1       ; touch down at origin
G01 X150 Y0         ; right
G01 X150 Y100       ; up
G01 X0 Y100         ; left
G01 X0 Y0           ; back to start
G00 X0 Y0 Z10       ; lift off
